data.description: Welcome to Edinburgh Square, an exclusive community that offers the perfect blend of luxury and comfort.This stunning 2 bed/2 bath condo boasts upgraded features including granite island, custom pantry shelving, lighting & flooring. The open-floor plan has ample natural light that pours in through the large windows & the gas fireplace adds a touch of warmth & comfort. Enjoy your favorite drink on 1 of 3 balconies or on the spacious front porch overlooking a picturesque pond & the greenway trail. The primary suite is a haven of relaxation, complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom featuring double sinks, a soaking tub & walk-in closet.The second bedroom can double as a home office has a large bathroom complete with a walk-in closet. In addition, this amazing condo comes with a large garage with extra storage space for all your needs. You'll love the convenience of living in the heart of Cornelius, close to shopping, restaurants & entertainment. Move in & Relax - Start living the dream!
